<div class="container-fluid">
		<div class="space-2"></div>

		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-xs-12">
				<div class="bordered-title">
					<h3>AMP iFrame</h3>
					<h5>Embed iFrames</h5>
				</div><!-- TITLE ENDS -->
			</div><!-- COL-XS-12 ENDS -->
		</div><!-- ROW ENDS -->

		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-xs-12">
				<p class="minus-margin-top-bottom-15">iFrames must be either 600px away from the top or not within the first 75% of the viewport when scrolled to the top â€“ whichever is smaller. This example might not work depending on your screen width. In this case it will only show an loading indicator.</p>

				<div class="space-3"></div>

				<h4 class="margin-0">Basic Usage</h4>

                <div class="space-2"></div>

                <amp-iframe width="500"
                    height="281"
                    layout="responsive"
                    sandbox="allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups"
                    allowfullscreen
                    frameborder="0"
                    src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/140261016">
                </amp-iframe>

				<div class="space-3"></div>

				<h4 class="margin-0">Using Placeholders</h4>
                <p>The 600px away from the top constraint can be avoided by adding a placeholder image.</p>

                <div class="space-2"></div>

                <amp-iframe width="500"
                            height="281"
                            layout="responsive"
                            sandbox="allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups"
                            allowfullscreen
                            frameborder="0"
                            src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/140261016">
                    <amp-img    layout="fill"
                                src="https://i.vimeocdn.com/video/536538454_640.webp"
                                placeholder></amp-img>
                </amp-iframe>

				<div class="space-3"></div>

				<h4 class="margin-0">Vimeo</h4>
                <p>If the video is 600px below the top, no placeholder image is required.</p>

                <div class="space-2"></div>

                <amp-iframe width="500"
                            height="281"
                            layout="responsive"
                            sandbox="allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups"
                            allowfullscreen
                            frameborder="0"
                            src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/140261016">
                </amp-iframe>

				<div class="space-3"></div>

				<h4 class="margin-0">Giphy</h4>

                <div class="space-2"></div>

                <amp-iframe width="600"
                            height="400"
                            layout="responsive"
                            sandbox="allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups"
                            frameborder="0"
                            src="https://giphy.com/embed/DKG1OhBUmxL4Q">
                </amp-iframe>

				<div class="space-3"></div>

				<h4 class="margin-0">Google Maps</h4>
                <p>Embedding Google Maps is possible via the <a href="https://developers.google.com/maps/documentation/embed/guide"><strong>Google Maps Embed API</strong></a> and requires an <a href="https://developers.google.com/maps/documentation/embed/guide#api_key"><strong>API Key</strong></a>.</p>

                <div class="space-2"></div>

                <amp-iframe width="600"
                            height="400"
                            layout="responsive"
                            sandbox="allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups"
                            frameborder="0"
                            src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed/v1/place?q=place_id:ChIJ2eUgeAK6j4ARbn5u_wAGqWA&key=AIzaSyCNCZ0Twm_HFRaZ5i-FuPDYs3rLwm4_848">
                </amp-iframe>
			</div><!-- COL-XS-12 ENDS -->
		</div><!-- ROW ENDS -->
	</div><!-- CONTAINER-FLUID ENDS -->

	{% include "templates/parts/_footer.nunjucks" %}